## Conventions Summary

| ✅ DO | ❌ DON'T |
|------|---------|
| Access the DB through the [detected] layer | Call the DB directly from the wrong layer |
| Eager-load related rows up front | Lazy-load inside loops (N+1) |
| Parameterize every query | Interpolate strings into SQL |
| Wrap related writes in one transaction | Save related records with separate calls |
| Soft-delete via `[deleted_at field]` | Hard-delete where soft delete is the convention |

